- content_for :jquery do
  = javascript_include_tag "jquery"
  = javascript_include_tag "jquery_ujs"
.home
  #flag.alert.alert-info.fw
    Welcome! You can start using one of ready-to-use assessments or create a test to suit your requirements!
    %br/
    You can use these assessments to measure behavior of your existing employee or potential hire that you are making.
    %a.close{:href => "#", :id => "close"}
      CLOSE
      %span.medium-text
        x
  .divider1

  .page-title.pull-left
    Ready-to-Send Assessments
  %button.btn.btn-warning.big-text.pull-right
    Create Custom Assessment
  .clr

  .divider1

  .big-text
    Choose the Assessment that comes close to the Job Role you want to measure.

  .divider2

  %ul.assessment-list.span28.margin-auto.clearfix
    %li
      %a.fw.span{:href => "#"}
        .pull-left
          Take the Assessment Yourself
        .icon-chevron-right.pull-right
    - if @standard_assessments.present?
      -@standard_assessments.each do |standard_assessment|
        / %h2
        /   = standard_assessment.attributes
        / -break
        %li
          %a.span7{:href => "#"}
            = standard_assessment.name
          .pull-right
            %a.icon-eye-open{:href => norms_standard_assessment_path(:id => standard_assessment.id)}
            %a.icon-file{:href => "#"}
            %a.icon-envelope{:href => "#"}
            .clr
          .clr
    - else
      %li
        %a.span8{:href => "#"}
          No Ready To Send Assessments Present
        .clr

  
  .divider3
  .info-list.span24.margin-auto.text-center
    .huge-text
      How it Works
    .divider4
    %ul.clearfix
      %li.span8
        .thumb1.divider5
        .big-text
          1. Choose Relevant Asessment
      %li.span8
        .thumb2.divider5
        .big-text
          2. See Assessment Details
      %li.span7
        .thumb3.divider5
        .big-text
          3. Send Assessment

  .divider4.border-bottom-grayLighter
  .divider2
  
  .benefit-list.span21.margin-auto.text-center
    .huge-text
      Benefits of Using Jombay
    .divider4
    %ul.clearfix
      %li.span5
        .thumb1.divider5
        .big-text
          Hire for the right Cultural Fit
      %li.span5
        .thumb2.divider5
        .big-text
          Reduce hiring errors
      %li.span5
        .thumb3.divider5
        .big-text
          Predict Attrition
      %li.span5
        .thumb4.divider5
        .big-text
          Identify Leadership Potential

  .divider2

:javascript
  $("#close").on('click',function(){
    $("#flag").hide(500);
  })

